  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a clay pot or heavy-bottomed pot over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté for 3 minutes until onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in sliced carrot and cubed sweet potato, cooking for 5 minutes.",
    "Add canned tomatoes, vegetable broth, cumin, paprika, salt, and pepper; stir to combine.",
    "Bring mixture to a gentle boil, then reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 25 minutes until vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in cooked chickpeas, cover, and simmer for another 10 minutes to let flavors meld.",
    "Remove from heat, squeeze lemon juice (optional) and stir in chopped cilantro for freshness.",
    "Serve hot with warm pita bread on the side."
  ],
